name: Datascape Beast Jiujiu
text:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
Cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects while you have 2 or more monsters with the same original Type and Attribute but different names in your GY. You can banish 2 monsters with the same original Type and Attribute but different names from your GY, then target 1 card on the field; send it to the GY. You can only use this effect of "Datascape Beast - Jiujiu" once per turn.
